{"title":"Norco Fluid VLT eMTB goes minimalist w/ multiple travel options","link":"https://bikerumor.com/norco-fluid-vlt-emtb-goes-minimalist-w-multiple-travel-options/","date":1687275479000,"content":"<p>Hot on the heels of the new Bosch Performance Line SX drive system, the Norco Fluid VLT comes in as light as 38lbs (17.24kg) by pairing it with a slim, full carbon frame.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That model is spec’d for minimum weight and runs 130mm rear travel with a 140mm fork, but three additional builds bump that to 140mm rear/150mm front and get a full carbon frame at the top, and two carbon/alloy blends at lower price points.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-5.jpg\" alt=\"motor details on norco fluid VLT lightweight e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-5.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-5-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-5-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Full specs and details are as slim as the frame for now, it doesn’t launch until Spring 2024, but here’s what we do know…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-4.jpg\" alt=\"norco fluid VLT lightweight e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-4.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-4-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-4-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-4-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-4-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It uses their Ride Aligned size-specific geometry, with rear center and seat tube angles changing along with the frame size to keep the rider sitting in the most balanced position.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-7.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-7.jpg\" alt=\"suspension details on norco fluid VLT lightweight e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-7.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-7-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-7-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-7-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-7-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-7-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It also uses Nroco’s popular and effective take on a Horst Link suspension, built around a 27.5″ rear wheel and 29er front. It’s a dedicated mixed wheel design, there’s no room to fit a 29er in the back.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-2.jpg\" alt=\"motor details on norco fluid VLT lightweight e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-2.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-2-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Inside the downtube is Bosch’s slim line 400Wh battery, and it’ll accept the 200Wh range extender for longer rides. 55Nm of assist helps you get up the longest climbs without taking all the “fun” of climbing away.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/norco-flow-app-customize-bosch-motor-settings.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1036\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/norco-flow-app-customize-bosch-motor-settings.jpg\" alt=\"app details on norco fluid VLT lightweight e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/norco-flow-app-customize-bosch-motor-settings.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/norco-flow-app-customize-bosch-motor-settings-297x160.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/norco-flow-app-customize-bosch-motor-settings-800x432.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/norco-flow-app-customize-bosch-motor-settings-120x65.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/norco-flow-app-customize-bosch-motor-settings-768x414.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/norco-flow-app-customize-bosch-motor-settings-1536x829.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Their custom Norco x Bosch Flow app lets you tweak the system’s output to maximize power or range, track your rides, see maintenance schedules, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-6.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-6.jpg\" alt=\"remote details on norco fluid VLT lightweight e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-6.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-6-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-6-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-6-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-6-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-1.jpg\" alt=\"frame details on norco fluid VLT lightweight e-mountain bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-1.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-1-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-norco-fluid-VLT-eMTB-bosch-SL-motor-1-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Claimed complete bike weights range from 38lbs to 44lbs, pricing and specs TBA.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.norco.com/fluid-vlt-gen-4\" target=\"_blank\">Norco.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/norco-fluid-vlt-emtb-goes-minimalist-w-multiple-travel-options/\">Norco Fluid VLT eMTB goes minimalist w/ multiple travel options</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb83700684